<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='922880' id='t-922880'>In architecture, it works just the same.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='925640' id='t-925640'>By appreciating the darkness
